---
title: One-Pan Pulled Pork & Chickpea Wraps with Cucumber Yogurt Salad
description: Pulled pork is big on flavor when you’re short on time. Here it stars in lunch-friendly shawarma-spiced wraps full of texture and flavor that come together in just 15 minutes. You'll warm up the pork with tender chickpeas and our shawarma-inspired blend of spices, then pile it into soft tortillas with a fresh, crunchy cucumber-tomato salad dressed in lemony yogurt sauce. Wrap it all up, and you’re ready to roll in no time at all!
